Package: xubuntu-gdm-theme
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, gdm
Recommends: gnome-settings-daemon, xfwm4
Suggests: xfce4-power-manager, xsplash
Conflicts: xubuntu-default-settings (<= 0.51), xsplash-artwork, xsplash (<< 0.8)
Replaces: xubuntu-default-settings (<= 0.51), xubuntu-artwork (<< 0.27~),
 xsplash-artwork, xsplash (<< 0.8)
Provides: gdm-theme, xsplash-artwork
Description: Xubuntu GDM & Xsplash greeter themes
 The GDM greeter theme used for a standalone Xubuntu installation.
 .
 This package can also be safely installed on other Ubuntu desktops desiring to
 use this theme.

Package: xubuntu-plymouth-theme
Architecture: all
Depends: plymouth-theme-xubuntu-logo
Description: Plymouth theme for Xubuntu - transitional package
 The Plymouth theme for Xubuntu.
 .
 This package can be safely removed.

Package: plymouth-theme-xubuntu-logo
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, plymouth, plymouth-label
Provides: plymouth-theme
Description: graphical boot animation and logger - xubuntu-logo theme
 Plymouth is an application that runs very early in the boot process (even
 before the root filesystem is mounted!) that provides a graphical boot
 animation while the boot process happens in the background.
 .
 This package contains the default xubuntu-logo theme.

Package: xubuntu-icon-theme
